The movies on blu-ray are very bright and also very clear. I am a huge fan of the
High School Musical movies and books.

Usually people like the original better than sequels.  But like highschool musical 3 the best, then 2, and 1 the worse.  I think the acting, signing, and dancing is definately the best by the time they do HSM3.

The whole family loves watching these movies.  My daughter (8 yrs old) of course loves them, but my son (5 yrs) also loves to watch.  He dances to all of the fast songs and they both try to sing along.  I like that they are something the whole family can watch together.  Sometimes I thought that in H.S. Musical 3 they barely had any dialogue before they had another song, but no one else seemed the least bit bothered by this.  Overall, the movies flow very well, have good underlying themes with important messages to kids on how to treat friends/other people and the characters are great!

I would just like to say that this order arrived alot faster than I thought it would. It was a birthday gift for a kid and I was sweating that it would make it on time and it arrived 6 days before I needed it.

I will buy all my movies from this company.
I got this combo set for a birthday present for my twin daughters.  They loved all the movies and were thrilled to get the whole collection at once.  Great purchase!
Great price for the trio of High School Musical in Blu-ray format.  Can't say anything else.  The movies were very entertaining for both kids and the kid at heart.
My kids had seen in a theater. Having them in blu-ray quality is like bringing the movie theater home.

I didn't realize what I was doing when I purchased these videos.  No one in my family has ever seen the movies prior to the purchase.  I can no longer say that.  My daughters are now addicted.  They love every moment of these movies.
This was an excellent purchase for my 12 year old...........She loved it and the xtended scenes are great.
Love that it has all three - BluRay, DVD and digital versions. Great idea so it can be watched in house or on the go.

It was great getting these all together. The only disappointing thing was that High School Musical 3 was not the extended version as 1 & 2. Otherwise a great deal!

These movies are What I've Been Looking For. The are Fabulous. I want to watch them Everyday. Zac Efron is adorable. Vanessa Hudgens is so cute. Of course the movies are cheesy but so fun to watch and sing along to. My favorite is High School Musical followed by HSM 3. HSM 2 is my least favorite but still a good movie. Classics that will stand the test of time. You need to buy these Right Here, Right Now. Bet On It.
